reviews.text:
Absolutely superb recipe. I made a 10mL tester and it was gone fairly quickly between my GF and I. All the flavours combine perfectly to make a spiced apple cider, and is hands down the best Apple Cider recipe I've come across. &#xD;
&#xD;
GF also loves it, and she's quite picky with her juices - so this is a 5/5 from me. Thanks for the amazing recipe Kind :)
